     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="3"/>
   <head>To the Reader.</head>
   <l>REade one, and say, tis good: I beare the name:</l>
   <l>Reade one, and say, tis ill, I beare the shame:</l>
   <l>If thou sayst, good, and think'st it too in heart,</l>
   <l>Sweetely farewell, no matter who thou art:</l>
   <l>If thou sayst, meane, thou iudgest like a frend,</l>
   <l>I would be so, because I meane to mend:</l>
   <l>If thou sayst, ill, and doost in heart dispraise it,</l>
   <l>I yeeld not till I know a Wiseman saies it.</l>
   <l>Thus quit me, or condemne me, Ile not grudge,</l>
   <l>So that I know a foole be not my Iudge.</l>
   <signed>Yours, William bas.</signed>
</div>
